- done ✅\\n6. `telegram:direct:6053576134` (Lead direct) - done ✅\\n7. `cron:b653a6c0` - zombie, stale ✅\\n8. `cron:ac986a8d` - zombie, stale ✅\\n9. Several subagents with failed/timeout status - pre-existing\\n10. `main` - done ✅\\n\\nThe cron:e7885813 session has some concerning notes about a delivery timeout trying to reach the Lead's Telegram, which suggests there might be connectivity issues I need to investigate further.\\n\\nLooking at the session history, there's a discrepancy: the e7885813 cron was supposedly reporting stable systems, but the latest message indicates a delivery timeout where it couldn't reach the target session. The target session (telegram:direct:6053576134) shows as \\\"done\\\" with an endedAt timestamp, which explains why the synchronous send failed—the session had already terminated and couldn't accept incoming messages.\\n\\nThe cron session continued processing after the timeout and exited, so the issue was logged but the session itself remained stable. Now comparing against the last heartbeat state from around 13:24 UTC, the critical sessions are still running: the 5p QLHV cron is active, the DTLX cron is active, and the Agent Status cron is running.\\n\\nChecking the current timestamp of 13:38 UTC, I can see cron:e7885813 did fire and updated its state, so there's been some activity in that session since the last check.\\n\\nLooking at the broader session landscape, the Agent Status cron encountered a delivery timeout when trying to reach the Lead's direct session, but that session was already done anyway—the message delivery was attempted after the fact. The cron itself continues running normally.\\n\\nThe key distinction here is that the timeout was a delivery attempt failure to an already-terminated session, not an actual system failure, so it's not a new blocker or critical issue worth reporting.\\n\\nNow I'm reviewing the session updates across the board—the cron jobs are firing normally on schedule, and the subagent failures are all pre-existing from previous runs with no new failures detected. The delivery timeout to Lead was already documented, so nothing here warrants a change report. I'll stay silent and update the heartbeat state.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Silent exit — no new changes detected. All sessions stable since last cycle.\\n\\n**Heartbeat state update:** 13:38 UTC, 3 active crons, no new failures, no new blockers. Pipeline healthy.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 30087,\n            \"output\": 661,\n            \"totalTokens\": 45108,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 416,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776173922677,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d7663ef93fe506148ed27b0486dce\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"1a99d2f4\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776173752157,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 148396,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776162044660,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776162158012,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 113352,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 13:34 UTC 14 Apr\\n\\nActive sessions: 3\\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p QLHV): running — 5-min progress monitoring (QLHV ecosystem) — ~3h 3m\\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p DTLX): running — 5-min progress monitoring (DTLX ecosystem) — ~9h 9m\\n• cron:e7885813 (Agent Status): running — Heartbeat monitor to Lead — ~2m\\n\\nPipeline: HEARTBEAT_OK ✅\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\n• No blockers. All critical monitors operational.\\n\\n— Orbis 🌐\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776173740874,\n          \"provenance\": {\n            \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n            \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n            \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n          },\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"5199e4e1\",\n            \"seq\": 1292\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Another heartbeat. Silent.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"HEARTBEAT_OK\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 281,\n            \"output\": 14,\n            \"totalTokens\": 148410,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 148115,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776173741058,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d75aea3738f236a825ba2e730326c\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"722df02d\",\n            \"seq\": 1293\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: Agent Status to Lead\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776173640019,\n      \"sessionId\": \"10369196-91e3-43d6-8942-b86dd7da9c97\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 23538,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776173053541,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/10369196-91e3-43d6-8942-b86dd7da9c97.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The session_send timed out. This means the target session is waiting for something. Let me check the session to see if it's still alive or if it's in a state that doesn't accept messages.\\n\\nActually, looking at the target session (telegram:direct:6053576134), it has status \\\"done\\\" and endedAt: 1776162158012. That session has ended. The delivery context was set to \\\"telegram:direct:6053576134\\\" but the session is done.\\n\\nHowever, since it's the direct session to Lead's Telegram, perhaps OpenClaw will still route the message to the Telegram channel even if the session is done. But the tool timed out.\\n \\nThe timeout likely occurred because the session is in a done state, so it can't process the message synchronously. The previous successful send at 13:24 UTC shows the delivery mechanism should work, but this session needs time to initialize and isn't immediately responsive.\\n\\nLooking at the session status, it shows \\\"done\\\" with an endedAt timestamp, which means it's not actively processing. This explains why the send timed out—the session might be in a waiting state or the delivery mechanism is hanging rather than the message failing outright. I should report this timeout to Lead as a delivery issue.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Delivery timed out — Lead's Telegram session was in a `done`/awaiting state and couldn't accept the synchronous send. The report will queue for next active window.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 178,\n            \"output\": 293,\n            \"totalTokens\": 23831,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14084,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 9276,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776173710355,\n          \"respons