us, it shows \"done\" with an endedAt timestamp, which means it's not actively processing. This explains why the send timed out—the session might be in a waiting state or the delivery mechanism is hanging rather than the message failing outright. I should report this timeout to Lead as a delivery issue."},{"type":"text","text":"Delivery timed out — Lead's Telegram session was in a `done`/awaiting state and couldn't accept the synchronous send. The report will queue for next active window."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":178,"output":293,"totalTokens":23831,"cacheRead":14084,"cacheWrite":9276,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776173710355,"responseId":"062d758f397ef2417533632b86c6e1da","__openclaw":{"id":"7e73775c","seq":6}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776171612342,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":67879,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776171601577,"endedAt":1776171610264,"runtimeMs":8687,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 12:31:58 UTC] Silent exit — no changes detected since last report (12:29 UTC). All monitored sessions stable. Pipeline healthy.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 12:34:09 UTC] Comparing current sessions against `heartbeat-state.json` (lastHeartbeat: 12:23 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Key sessions:**\nSystem: - `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running, still active (12:21 UTC)\nSystem: - `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running, still active (12:28 UTC) — this cron\nS